name: Doge-1 Mission to the moon
description: Doge-1 mission to the moon is a BEP20 token that provides rewards in DOGE. As a community token Doge-1 has many things to offer starting with the development of a high end NFT marketplace that will change the way you interact with NFT's. This team has been assembled by some of the most experienced developers in the BSC space from all over the world, all very excited to bring new developments to Doge-1 Mission to the Moon.
